ttp://www.otakuusamagazine.com/puella-magi-madoka-magica-rebellion-review/|archivedate=2017-09-30 }}</ref>。來自THEM Anime Reviews的徹盧西（Jacob Churosh）進一步提出「儘管[[悠木碧|悠木碧]]的鹿目圓也很出色，但[[齋藤千和|齋藤千和]]的曉美焰更勝一籌，其孤高冷酷的假面以驚人的速度崩潰後，導致她自我偽裝的悲劇根源引人不住深掘。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themanime.org/viewreview.php?id=1352|title=''Puella Magi Madoka Magica''|first=Jacob|last=Churosh|website=THEM Anime Reviews|accessdate=2017-09-06|archive-date=2017-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170907000904/http://www.themanime.org/viewreview.php?id=1352|dead-url=no}}</ref>」；瓊斯（Tim Jones）補充道「焰與[[佐倉杏子|杏子]]擁有本系列最發達的背景故事」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themanime.org/viewreview.php?id=1243|title=''Puella Magi Madoka Magica''|first=Tim|last=Jones|website=THEM Anime Reviews|accessdate=2017-09-06|archive-date=2017-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906233546/http://www.themanime.org/viewreview.php?id=1243|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]網站的安納斯塔西奧（Cecilia D'Anastasio）認為「曉美焰是最棒的女孩」「她擁有許多美德，像是力量與同情心」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/the-hair-flips-of-madoka-magica-s-homura-ranked-1792236680|title=The Hair Flips Of Madoka Magica’s Homura, Ranked|first=Cecilia|last=D'Anastasio|publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|date=2017-02-10|accessdate=2017-09-06|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170907033335/https://kotaku.com/the-hair-flips-of-madoka-magica-s-homura-ranked-1792236680|archivedate=2017-09-07 }}</ref>。其他評論家如艾森拜斯（Richard Eisenbeis）指稱，基於曲折的情節與人物動機，重看本作便會「發現一個屬於曉美焰的、而非鹿目圓的嶄新故事」，他認為焰相當於「一個瘋狂世界中唯一理智的人」，其台詞往往具有雙重含意，唯有二度觀賞才能去體會<ref name=Eisenbeis>{{cite web|url=https://kotaku.com/the-new-modoka-magica-movie-is-the-sequel-you-never-kne-1453844468|title=The New Madoka Magica Movie is the Sequel You Never Knew Was Needed|first=Richard|last=Einsenbeis|publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|date=2013-10-29|accessdate=2018-01-01|archive-date=2018-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180102073535/https://kotaku.com/the-new-modoka-magica-movie-is-the-sequel-you-never-kne-1453844468|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

